{"tid":1737450,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"國際陣線應該要打呢樣野","createTime":"2019-11-19T03:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T03:47:43.000Z","uid":76957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bacb4588097d2d15f6c7420a40306ec5324bae2","tid":1737450,"uid":76957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:17:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_4995046?from=groupmessage&amp;fbclid=IwAR3CNQt0MWE6tgvaakIDrrqH8v29VFcHcKFVSQA-N6l-jGUY1No3R7oeYBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.thepaper.cn%2FnewsDetail_forward_4995046%3Ffrom%3Dgroupmessage%26fbclid%3DIwAR3CNQt0MWE6tgvaakIDrrqH8v29VFcHcKFVSQA-N6l-jGUY1No3R7oeYBY&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=583b2a26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_4995046?from=groupmessage&amp;fbclid=IwAR3CNQt0MWE6tgvaakIDrrqH8v29VFcHcKFVSQA-N6l-jGUY1No3R7oeYBY</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;我们正在研究一些全国人大代表提出的有关意见和建议。&quot;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n國際上 我地需要強烈地比西方國家知道<br />\n法治危機已經黎到<br />\n令到佢地睇實中共<br />\n推到佢地當一旦人大再釋法 會肯做制裁<br />\n要明白司法獨立係香港最重要既精神<br />\n係因為咁先可以做到金融自由港<br />\n一旦法治精神完全被破壞 一定要攬炒<br />\n一定要比國際知<br />\n<br />\nbtw 而家國際戰線係主打人道牌<br />\n其實係好 係多人留意 有民心 多支持 理應同時繼續打<br />\n但係始終<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">好現實 國家政府做事係睇利益</span></span><br />\n所以你講民主自由 除非又有六四 否則國際社會幫極有限<br />\n出師冇名之餘 又唔係真係有極大人道危機<br />\n所以話佢地知 佢地再唔發威比中共睇 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就會有經濟損失</span></span><br />\n認同既 麻煩幫手推一推"},{"pid":"4e80fe2b6e0ab04fbde4b36be452ba093640050f","tid":1737450,"uid":76957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:21:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"48c8999b3df515629d11ef1917c90cf76c99a48c","tid":1737450,"uid":76957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5122c4e4504b9dfda26e0e6fa002e773403c3fca","tid":1737450,"uid":76957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0daa6c1277b0c9f692608990b84d7a019aba3d25","tid":1737450,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:40:55.000Z","msg":"18-8-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33c967c05b68a97f8070024a79f0360bb43607e6","tid":1737450,"uid":76957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"要令其他政府做野<br />\n就要引發更多輿論<br />\n咁就要係國際上推呢樣野"},{"pid":"89192d23f8ed2cc57482cbd29a004bc223e5248a","tid":1737450,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:47:43.000Z","msg":"推"}]}